NAIROBI, Kenya, January 23, 2020/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            The Minister of Foreign Affairs of Cuba, Bruno Rodr√≠guez Parrilla, sent his congratulations to Ambassador Monica Juma, on the occasion of her appointment as Cabinet Secretary of the Ministry of Defense of Kenya.



